<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Delivered</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9ecc2; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(123,49,22,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7b3116 0%, #9d4421 100%); color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; margin: -20px -20px 20px -20px; }
        .celebration { font-size: 48px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .order-info { background-color: #f9ecc2; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #7b3116; }
        .order-info h3 { color: #7b3116; margin-top: 0; }
        .order-items { margin: 20px 0; }
        .item { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f9ecc2; }
        .item img { width: 60px; height: 60px; object-fit: cover; margin-right: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border: 2px solid #f9ecc2; }
        .item-details { flex: 1; }
        .item-name { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #7b3116; }
        .item-price { color: #666; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9ecc2 0%, #fdf5d9 100%); color: #7b3116; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; margin: 10px 5px; font-weight: bold; border: 2px solid #7b3116; }
        .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7b3116 0%, #9d4421 100%); color: white; border: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(123,49,22,0.3); }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 2px solid #f9ecc2; }
        .footer a { color: #7b3116; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Order Delivered Successfully! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
            <p>Your order has reached you safely, {{customerName}}!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="celebration">ðŸš›âœ¨ðŸ“¦</div>

        <div class="order-info">
            <h3>Delivery Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Order Number:</strong> {{orderNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> {{orderDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Delivery Date:</strong> {{deliveryDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> â‚¹{{totalAmount}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="order-items">
            <h3 style="color: #7b3116;">Items Delivered</h3>
            {{#each orderItems}}
            <div class="item">
                <div style="width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-right: 15px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                    {{#if image}}
                    <img src="{{image}}" alt="{{name}}" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #f9ecc2; display: block;">
                    {{else}}
                    <div style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9ecc2 0%, #fdf5d9 100%); border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #7b3116; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #7b3116; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;">
                        ðŸ“¦<br>Product
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                <div class="item-details">
                    <div class="item-name">{{name}}</div>
                    <div class="item-price">Quantity: {{quantity}} Ã— â‚¹{{price}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <h3>How was your experience?</h3>
            <p>We'd love to hear about your experience with this order!</p>
            <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="btn">Rate & Review</a>
            <a href="{{storeUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">Shop Again</a>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;">
            <h3>Thank You for Shopping With Us!</h3>
            <p>We hope you love your purchase. Your satisfaction is our priority.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>Visit our store: <a href="{{storeUrl}}">{{storeUrl}}</a></p>
            <p>Â© 2024 Your Store. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>